UINT8_MAX
===
> Maximum unsigned 8-bit integer.

<!-- <usage> -->
## Usage

``` javascript
var UINT8_MAX = require( '@stdlib/math/constants/uint8-max' );
```

#### UINT8_MAX

Maximum unsigned 8-bit integer.

``` javascript
UINT8_MAX === Math.pow( 2, 8 ) - 1;
```
<!-- </usage> -->

<!-- <examples> -->
## Examples

``` javascript
var UINT8_MAX = require( '@stdlib/math/constants/uint8-max' );

console.log( UINT8_MAX );
// returns 255
```
<!-- </examples> -->
